It's fine.

10
00:01:49,550 --> 00:01:50,550
You can drink mine now.

11
00:01:50,590 --> 00:01:52,830
It contains red dates and goji berries,

12
00:01:52,830 --> 00:01:53,510
and other ingredients.

13
00:01:54,160 --> 00:01:55,510
Drink it to warm up.

14
00:01:55,830 --> 00:01:56,800
Then have some chicken soup

15
00:01:57,510 --> 00:01:58,400
to nourish your body.

16
