Please sit.

17
00:02:03,680 --> 00:02:04,480
Be careful.

18
00:02:04,480 --> 00:02:05,270
Thanks.

19
00:02:17,880 --> 00:02:18,670
Have a try.

20
00:02:27,520 --> 00:02:28,440
Is your name Luo Shu

21
00:02:28,440 --> 00:02:29,720
or Luo Shuxiang?

22
00:02:35,880 --> 00:02:36,830
What do you mean?

23
00:02:37,800 --> 00:02:38,440
Jin Nang.

24
00:02:40,110 --> 00:02:40,800
I didn't expect you

25
00:02:40,800 --> 00:02:42,080
to be Jin Nang from Mingke House.

26
00:02:42,800 --> 00:02:44,470
We have quite a connection, don't we?

27
00:02:44,600 --> 00:02:46,000
I thought you were so far away,

28
00:02:46,270 --> 00:02:47,520
but you are right in front of me.

29
00:02:48,190 --> 00:02:49,600
Why didn't you tell me earlier?

30
00:02:49,720 --> 00:02:50,440
You even deliberately let me

31
00:02:50,440 --> 00:02:51,440
introduce you to Jin Nang.

32
00:02:51,600 --> 00:02:52,880
You just wanted to embarrass me, right?

33
00:02:53,440 --> 00:02:54,190
I went to Mingke House

34
00:02:54,190 --> 00:02:55,470
in the morning to invite Jin Nang,

35
00:02:56,390 --> 00:02:57,550
sorry, Miss Luo.

36
00:02:58,830 --> 00:02:59,670
But when I got there,

37
00:02:59,670 --> 00:03:00,030
they said

38
00:03:00,030 --> 00:03:01,360
Miss Luo had redeemed herself.

39
00:03:02,270 --> 00:03:03,670
I thought, since I was there,

40
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:04,800
I didn't want to

41
00:03:04,800 --> 00:03:05,750
let you down,

42
00:03:06,270 --> 00:03:07,360
so I invited

43
00:03:07,360 --> 00:03:08,880
the Five Beauties of Mingke.

44
00:03:09,360 --> 00:03:10,800
They were all on the boat just now.

45
00:03:11,880 --> 00:03:13,670
Why didn't you say hi to them?

46
00:03:15,000 --> 00:03:15,800
Right,

47
00:03:15,880 --> 00:03:17,440
you were scared just now.

48
00:03:17,750 --> 00:03:18,550
By the way,

49
00:03:19,190 --> 00:03:20,360
you recognized me

50
00:03:20,910 --> 00:03:21,880
in the jail that day,

51
00:03:21,880 --> 00:03:22,390
didn't you?

52
00:03:23,910 --> 00:03:24,470
I did.

53
00:03:24,470 --> 00:03:25,750
Then why didn't you say it?

54
00:03:26,000 --> 00:03:27,750
Why would I do that?

55
00:03:28,110 --> 00:03:29,630
Mr. Qi, thanks for reminding me

56
00:03:30,110 --> 00:03:31,630
of my origin in the Music House

57
00:03:31,960 --> 00:03:33,470
and that I am lowborn.

58
00:03:33,470 --> 00:03:34,190
No.

59
00:03:34,190 --> 00:03:34,550
Why do you think

60
00:03:34,550 --> 00:03:35,910
I changed my name,

61
00:03:36,240 --> 00:03:37,880
and disguised myself as a man?

62
00:03:37,960 --> 00:03:38,630
Why do you think

63
00:03:38,630 --> 00:03:40,240
I became a constable?

64
00:03:40,630 --> 00:03:42,080
It's because I don't want to
have connection

65
00:03:42,080 --> 00:03:43,390
with my past anymore.

66
00:03:43,910 --> 00:03:45,600
Yet you keep reminding me,

67
00:03:45,600 --> 00:03:46,320
forcing me to admit

68
00:03:46,320 --> 00:03:47,750
that I am from the Music House.

69
00:03:47,800 --> 00:03:49,000
I didn't mean to degrade you.

70
00:03:49,000 --> 00:03:50,670
I just think it's amazing
that we have this connection.

71
00:03:51,550 --> 00:03:53,270
Mr. Qi, you're so precious.

72
00:03:53,360 --> 00:03:55,240
How could we have a connection?

73
00:03:58,320 --> 00:03:59,160
Just get out of here.

74
00:03:59,160 --> 00:04:00,440
Someone as lowly as me

75
00:04:00,440 --> 00:04:01,470
will taint your reputation.

76
00:04:02,670 --> 00:04:03,270
I...

77
00:04:04,750 --> 00:04:05,470
I didn't say anything

78
00:04:05,470 --> 00:04:06,750
and you just get mad out of the blue.

79
00:04:07,110 --> 00:04:08,630
What did I say to insult you?

80
00:04:09,320 --> 00:04:10,470
You just tell me.

81
00:04:10,750 --> 00:04:11,830
I really don't understand

82
00:04:12,080 --> 00:04:13,030
why you get angry.

83
00:04:13,360 --> 00:04:14,910
With your noble status,

84
00:04:15,550 --> 00:04:16,440
you will never understand

85
00:04:16,440 --> 00:04:17,670
the thoughts of us lowly folk.

86
00:04:18,350 --> 00:04:19,640
If I really thought you that way,

87
00:04:19,640 --> 00:04:20,440
I wouldn't have spent

88
00:04:20,440 --> 00:04:21,550
five hundred and one liang for you.

89
00:04:23,160 --> 00:04:25,160
You are wealthy,

90
00:04:25,440 --> 00:04:26,160
of course

91
00:04:26,160 --> 00:04:27,160
you don't care about

92
00:04:27,160 --> 00:04:27,880
five hundred and one liang.

93
00:04:27,880 --> 00:04:29,320
That's not what I meant.

94
00:04:29,320 --> 00:04:31,230
I was a performer in the Music House.

95
00:04:33,040 --> 00:04:34,480
I had no choice.

96
00:04:36,040 --> 00:04:37,720
I once ended up in Mingke House.

97
00:04:38,230 --> 00:04:39,670
God was unfair.

98
00:04:40,390 --> 00:04:41,230
God was being unfair to you.

99
00:04:41,230 --> 00:04:42,110
I was not.

100
00:04:42,110 --> 00:04:43,040
Don't get angry with me.

101
00:04:43,040 --> 00:04:44,160
I sympathize with you.

102
00:04:44,160 --> 00:04:45,670
I don't need that.

103
00:04:46,760 --> 00:04:48,720
Mind your own business.

104
00:04:49,390 --> 00:04:50,480
You're just gold without
and rubbish within.

105
00:04:50,480 --> 00:04:51,720
A worthless good-for-nothing.

106
00:04:51,920 --> 00:04:52,550
I...

107
00:04:53,350 --> 00:04:54,440
You call me good-for-nothing?

108
00:04:55,550 --> 00:04:57,040
Although you have a noble status,

109
00:04:57,110 --> 00:04:58,510
you use your father's name,

110
00:04:58,510 --> 00:05:00,230
showing off in public and
spending lavishly.

111
00:05:00,480 --> 00:05:01,830
You have no ambition, no knowledge,

112
00:05:01,830 --> 00:05:02,880
yet always feel self-satisfied.

113
00:05:03,270 --> 00:05:04,110
People like you

114
00:05:04,110 --> 00:05:05,200
are so pathetic.

115
00:05:26,320 --> 00:05:27,110
White Fan.

116
00:05:34,670 --> 00:05:35,760
The woman we kidnapped additionally

117
00:05:35,760 --> 00:05:36,670
has been rescued,

118
00:05:36,670 --> 00:05:38,550
but Qiao Ruolan has not been found yet.

119
00:05:39,920 --> 00:05:40,720
Are you sure?

120
00:05:40,720 --> 00:05:41,230
Yes.

121
00:05:41,230 --> 00:05:42,270
I hid nearby for a long time

122
00:05:42,270 --> 00:05:43,320
to observe.

123
00:05:45,880 --> 00:05:47,950
What about Bai Er?

124
00:05:48,160 --> 00:05:49,920
You don't need to worry about them.

125
00:05:55,040 --> 00:05:56,480
Leave the city and hide.

126
00:05:57,160 --> 00:05:57,670
Got it.

127
00:06:00,820 --> 00:06:02,580
[The secret recipe of Jinrui Liquor]

128
00:06:03,720 --> 00:06:05,350
Qiao Ruolan should have drowned already.

129
00:06:07,480 --> 00:06:10,000
Great, great.

130
00:06:15,230 --> 00:06:16,230
Now that she's dead,

131
00:06:16,720 --> 00:06:18,320
no one will cause me trouble anymore.

132
00:06:20,670 --> 00:06:21,830
With this secret recipe,

133
00:06:22,070 --> 00:06:23,440
the liquor distillery

134
00:06:24,480 --> 00:06:26,670
will truly be my cash cow.

135
00:06:30,230 --> 00:06:31,000
By then...

136
00:06:32,760 --> 00:06:33,790
What, yours?

137
00:06:34,790 --> 00:06:35,230
This secret recipe.

138
00:06:35,230 --> 00:06:36,390
I had to sacrifice two of my men

139
00:06:36,390 --> 00:06:36,880
to get it.

140
00:06:38,920 --> 00:06:39,830
It's time to start the brewing process.

141
00:06:41,040 --> 00:06:42,200
Take over the business

142
00:06:42,720 --> 00:06:43,830
completely

143
00:06:44,550 --> 00:06:45,720
to avoid complications.

144
00:06:46,000 --> 00:06:46,640
Okay.

145
00:06:49,390 --> 00:06:50,790
Will they

146
00:06:50,790 --> 00:06:51,920
snitch on you?

147
00:06:54,440 --> 00:06:55,350
They don't know anything.

148
00:06:55,950 --> 00:06:56,550
Okay.

149
00:06:57,550 --> 00:06:58,880
Good.

150
00:07:14,550 --> 00:07:15,350
Say it or not?

151
00:07:16,070 --> 00:07:16,920
Say it or not?

152
00:07:17,920 --> 00:07:18,790
Say it!

153
00:07:19,000 --> 00:07:20,760
Your Honor, please.

154
00:07:21,110 --> 00:07:23,000
I'll confess!

155
00:07:23,670 --> 00:07:24,480
Say it.

156
00:07:25,230 --> 00:07:26,040
We are indeed

157
00:07:26,230 --> 00:07:27,670
from the White Ant.

158
00:07:27,920 --> 00:07:29,320
Normally,

159
00:07:29,920 --> 00:07:31,350
we are decent boatmen.

160
00:07:31,670 --> 00:07:34,040
When we receive an order,

161
00:07:34,270 --> 00:07:35,350
we follow through on it.

162
00:07:35,550 --> 00:07:36,790
Have you been involved in
murder, robbery,

163
00:07:37,760 --> 00:07:39,760
and trafficking in women?

164
00:07:40,160 --> 00:07:41,160
We haven't killed anyone.

165
00:07:42,880 --> 00:07:44,000
Just kidnapped women.

166
00:07:46,550 --> 00:07:47,390
Kidnapped women?

167
00:07:48,230 --> 00:07:49,040
Hit!

168
00:07:56,640 --> 00:07:57,510
Please.

169
00:07:57,790 --> 00:07:59,600
Please stop, Your Honor.

170
00:07:59,950 --> 00:08:02,600
Tell me, who sent you to do this?

171
00:08:02,790 --> 00:08:03,760
White Fan.

172
00:08:03,790 --> 00:08:04,920
Who's White Fan?

173
00:08:04,920 --> 00:08:06,720
White Fan is White Fan.

174
00:08:07,070 --> 00:08:07,950
Hit!

175
00:08:08,200 --> 00:08:09,270
White Fan

176
00:08:09,270 --> 00:08:11,070
is second in charge in the White Ant.

177
00:08:11,510 --> 00:08:13,920
We don't usually see him.

178
00:08:14,760 --> 00:08:16,440
All we know is his name,

179
00:08:16,670 --> 00:08:18,510
nothing else.

180
00:08:20,000 --> 00:08:20,790
Alright.

181
00:08:28,720 --> 00:08:30,390
Who put his hands

182
00:08:30,390 --> 00:08:31,550
on our female constable today?

183
00:08:32,960 --> 00:08:33,590
Say it!

184
00:08:34,910 --> 00:08:36,470
It was him!

185
00:08:36,470 --> 00:08:37,910
I didn't do anything!

186
00:08:37,960 --> 00:08:38,710
I...

187
00:08:40,350 --> 00:08:40,840
No.

188
00:08:43,640 --> 00:08:44,280
It wasn't me.

189
00:08:47,440 --> 00:08:48,400
Take him back to the jail.

190
00:08:51,320 --> 00:08:52,350
He stays.

191
00:08:52,910 --> 00:08:54,000
Continue.

192
00:08:54,400 --> 00:08:56,150
Your Honor, please spare me.

193
00:08:56,440 --> 00:08:57,790
I wasn't me, Your Honor.

194
00:08:58,110 --> 00:08:59,110
Please, Your Honor.

195
00:08:59,110 --> 00:09:00,320
I don't know anything!

196
00:09:00,320 --> 00:09:00,910
Your Honor.

197
00:09:04,960 --> 00:09:05,910
Muzhi.

198
00:09:05,960 --> 00:09:07,110
You're the magistrate.

199
00:09:07,110 --> 00:09:08,350
How can you interrogate criminals,

200
00:09:08,350 --> 00:09:09,880
especially in the jail?

201
00:09:10,230 --> 00:09:11,790
What's the background of the White Ant?

202
00:09:13,760 --> 00:09:15,080
Nothing special.

203
00:09:15,280 --> 00:09:16,550
Just a bunch of gangsters,

204
00:09:16,550 --> 00:09:18,030
specializing in kidnapping women.

205
00:09:19,030 --> 00:09:21,150
They make a living like ordinary people
in normal days.

206
00:09:21,200 --> 00:09:23,200
It's difficult to distinguish them,

207
00:09:23,230 --> 00:09:25,230
not to mention suppressing them.

208
00:09:25,880 --> 00:09:26,670
Actually,

209
00:09:27,110 --> 00:09:29,080
they've been terrorizing in Linfen

210
00:09:29,400 --> 00:09:30,520
for over a decade.

211
00:09:31,000 --> 00:09:31,960
Over a decade?

212
00:09:32,670 --> 00:09:33,880
And no one has brought them to justice?

213
00:09:34,200 --> 00:09:35,320
About six years ago,

214
00:09:35,440 --> 00:09:37,440
a provincial governor
wanted to clean them up.

215
00:09:37,440 --> 00:09:38,910
He came to Linfen to supervise.

216
00:09:38,960 --> 00:09:40,590
Dozens of White Ants

217
00:09:40,590 --> 00:09:42,030
were waiting in ambush
on a bustling street.

218
00:09:42,350 --> 00:09:43,760
When his carriage passed by,

219
00:09:43,760 --> 00:09:45,030
they swarmed out.

220
00:09:45,030 --> 00:09:46,470
Before the officials could react,

221
00:09:46,470 --> 00:09:48,590
the provincial governor was pulled off

222
00:09:48,640 --> 00:09:50,960
and got a series of slaps in the face.

223
00:09:51,110 --> 00:09:52,880
His face swelled up like a pig's head.

224
00:09:53,470 --> 00:09:55,320
Then they scattered in an instant.

225
00:09:55,960 --> 00:09:56,910
The provincial governor

226
00:09:57,030 --> 00:09:58,440
not only lost his hearing,

227
00:09:58,440 --> 00:10:00,080
but also couldn't continue his duty.

228
00:10:00,080 --> 00:10:01,590
He had to retire

229
00:10:01,790 --> 00:10:04,520
and became a complete laughingstock.

230
00:10:06,150 --> 00:10:08,030
I've heard about that.

231
00:10:08,230 --> 00:10:09,280
So,

232
00:10:09,590 --> 00:10:10,550
don't think about

233
00:10:10,550 --> 00:10:11,640
capturing them anymore.

234
00:10:16,640 --> 00:10:17,520
That's ridiculous.

235
00:10:19,880 --> 00:10:20,910
She pushed me too far.

236
00:10:21,550 --> 00:10:22,880
Why did she scold me?

237
00:10:23,760 --> 00:10:25,910
You insulted her first.

238
00:10:26,350 --> 00:10:26,840
What?

239
00:10:27,840 --> 00:10:29,200
I said you were right.

240
00:10:29,280 --> 00:10:30,520
She wronged me.

241
00:10:30,760 --> 00:10:32,590
When did I ever treat people differently
because of their status?

242
00:10:32,590 --> 00:10:33,150
Over time,

243
00:10:33,150 --> 00:10:34,440
she'll know how great you are.

244
00:10:34,440 --> 00:10:35,280
Of course.

245
00:10:37,000 --> 00:10:37,840
Scold me, huh?

246
00:10:38,400 --> 00:10:39,200
Alright,

247
00:10:39,880 --> 00:10:40,910
you better do not regret.

248
00:10:43,470 --> 00:10:44,280
Yeah.

249
00:10:45,080 --> 00:10:46,790
I'll leave.

250
00:10:47,110 --> 00:10:48,400
Let's see what she'll do without me.

251
00:10:48,790 --> 00:10:49,960
Lian Shu,

252
00:10:50,150 --> 00:10:51,670
go to tell everyone in the county yamen,

253
00:10:51,670 --> 00:10:53,150
especially the one surnamed Luo,

254
00:10:54,150 --> 00:10:54,880
that I'm gonna leave Linfen

255
00:10:54,960 --> 00:10:55,960
and will never come back.

256
00:10:57,230 --> 00:10:58,470
Young Master, are you serious?

257
00:10:58,960 --> 00:10:59,880
Just go.

258
00:11:05,740 --> 00:11:08,660
[Linfen Yamen]

259
00:11:13,150 --> 00:11:13,960
Young Master.

260
00:11:14,280 --> 00:11:15,280
How's it?

261
00:11:15,790 --> 00:11:16,670
What's her reaction?

262
00:11:16,840 --> 00:11:17,960
She said, "Oh."

263
00:11:18,440 --> 00:11:18,960
Oh?

264
00:11:19,200 --> 00:11:19,640
Oh.

265
00:11:19,960 --> 00:11:20,760
Oh?

266
00:11:20,960 --> 00:11:22,030
That's it? Then what?

267
00:11:22,550 --> 00:11:23,840
Then I came back.

268
00:11:28,790 --> 00:11:29,960
She pushed me too far.

269
00:11:31,910 --> 00:11:33,760
Great. You want to stay cool, huh?

270
00:11:33,960 --> 00:11:34,790
I can also be cool.

271
00:11:35,230 --> 00:11:37,400
Lian Shu, go to pack up.

272
00:11:38,030 --> 00:11:38,840
Yes, Young Master.

273
00:11:39,960 --> 00:11:40,760
Lian Shu,

274
00:11:41,520 --> 00:11:43,150
make sure you've packed up everything.

275
00:11:43,840 --> 00:11:45,640
My hairpin,

276
00:11:45,880 --> 00:11:46,710
put it away.

277
00:11:46,760 --> 00:11:48,080
And those Liulin Red Dates,

278
00:11:48,110 --> 00:11:48,910
pack them up too.

279
00:11:49,440 --> 00:11:50,840
I'll give to the girls at home

280
00:11:50,840 --> 00:11:52,000
and let them have a good taste.

281
00:11:53,470 --> 00:11:54,280
And the horse,

282
00:11:55,030 --> 00:11:56,790
make sure it's well-fed.

283
00:11:57,230 --> 00:11:59,000
We'll have a long ride

284
00:11:59,000 --> 00:12:00,150
back to Taiyuan tomorrow.

285
00:12:02,670 --> 00:12:03,470
Young Master,

286
00:12:03,710 --> 00:12:05,440
I don't think they can hear you.

287
00:12:08,400 --> 00:12:08,910
Just pack up.

288
00:12:13,790 --> 00:12:14,960
I'm getting hypoxic.

289
00:12:16,910 --> 00:12:17,710
I will leave.

290
00:12:18,470 --> 00:12:19,200
Our men

291
00:12:19,200 --> 00:12:20,760
are still searching
along the river bank.

292
00:12:21,640 --> 00:12:22,440
Your Honor,

293
00:12:22,670 --> 00:12:23,670
we've searched all night,

294
00:12:23,790 --> 00:12:24,840
